    <PrimAttribute name="checkingSecondary" id="78a31515-ae21-44dd-a656-ce6aaf4fe8e2">
        <embedded/>
        <type name="Boolean"/>
        <text>This is set when we are checking secondary locations for
tests. For example the arse end of a 40' container. Because
a lot of the test methods do this check at the same time, they
use the same code, but set this flag so they dont recurse
forever.</text>
    </PrimAttribute>
