    <PrimAttribute name="iteration" id="0cd7c041-5328-4ce6-9554-71ed4f917832">
        <embedded/>
        <type name="Integer"/>
        <text>This is only valid for straddle stack planning.
The users have the ability to select which direction stacking is
to progress (up, or along). If we are stacking ALONG the row, then we need
to iterate along the row for each height in the stack.
This is the controlling property that tells the method which
height we are currently working on.</text>
    </PrimAttribute>
